{"article_id":"cMJmrY4kQi9DpuaB","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"No doubt many pundits in the media world will declare Republican Gov . Mike Pence of Indiana the winner of Tuesday night 's vice presidential debate against Democratic Sen. Tim Kaine of Virginia .","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"Kaine was admittedly overexcited","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"and his constant interrupting of Pence in the first 20 minutes rubbed everyone , on the left and right , the wrong way .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"Meanwhile , Pence exuded the preternatural calm of a sociopath ,","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"increasingly frustrating Kaine with his ability","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"to endlessly lie","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"- about easily checked facts -","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"with a disturbingly practiced assurance .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"But","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"while Kaine did n't win any points on likability ,","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"he had a job to do","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"and he got it done :","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"pushing out the anti-Trump talking points","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"and highlighting the vast differences between Hillary Clinton campaign 's vision for racial justice versus the Trump campaign 's overt racism and bigotry .","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"On that front , Kaine got the job done .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"He repeatedly dragged the conversation back to issues about racial justice , from policing to immigration ,","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"which worked to put Pence on the defensive","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"while appealing to black and Latino voters","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"( and anyone , really ,","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"who cares about racial justice ) .","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"While Pence was the living embodiment of an unflappable liar","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"- definitely the guy","depth":14},{"id":22,"text":"to go to","depth":14},{"id":23,"text":"if you need someone","depth":14},{"id":24,"text":"to bury the bodies -","depth":14},{"id":25,"text":"Kaine 's relentlessness on this front clearly got to him enough","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"that , for a brief , shining moment , he got flustered and angry .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"\" You whipped out that Mexican thing again , ''","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"Pence whined .","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"It was one of the few memorable lines of the night","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"and the likeliest to grab headlines .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"No doubt Latino viewers","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"watching the debate","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"took notice .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"Kaine was irritating ,","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"but Pence was downright creepy .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"Many of the lies","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"he told","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"do n't need fact-checking","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"to be read as such :","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"Denying Trump 's bigotry ,","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"denying his and Trump 's praise of Vladimir Putin ,","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"pretending","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"that it 's Clinton and not Trump who is running an `` insult-driven campaign ''","depth":14},{"id":44,"text":"as he put it .","depth":14},{"id":45,"text":"People","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"who look you in the eye","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"and lie so boldly","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"without breaking a sweat","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"are creepy ,","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"and I 'm sure","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"voters noticed that .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"It does n't help that Pence has a disturbing affect ,","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"which is made all the worse by his tendency","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"to crack deeply unfunny jokes","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"and then act really pleased with himself","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"like he 's charming and not creepy .","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"He even tried to roll out Ronald Reagan 's `` there you go again '' line","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"and did n't seem to notice","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"that he could n't sell it at all .","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"He is clearly a man","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"who has spent his life mistaking people 's polite laughter for genuine merriment ,","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"and that inability","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"to read other people","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"comes across as , well , creepy .","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"Let 's just say","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"that few people","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"who watched that debate","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"are going to welcome further interactions with the governor of Indiana .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"Kaine scored some good points towards the second half of the debate .","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"After Pence rolled out some dishonest talking points about the Clinton Foundation ,","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"Kaine countered this perfectly","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"by highlighting the foundation 's good work","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"and contrasting it with the sleazy goings-on surrounding Trump 's foundation and business organizations ,","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"even managing to inject Trump 's boy crush on Putin into the proceedings .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"Later","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"when the topic of abortion came up ,","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"Pence became passionate for the first time ,","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"which led him awfully close to suggesting","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"that women should be forced to give birth","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"so that strangers","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"who want their babies","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"can have them .","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"Again , that reads more as creepy than as `` pro-life . ''","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"But Kaine went in for the kill shot ,","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"asserting","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"that his pro-choice views were rooted in his belief in religious freedom","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"and demanding to know","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"why Pence does n't trust women .","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"Pence could only answer with empty pablum .","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"Vice presidential debates do n't really move the needle of public opinion .","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"The only thing","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"campaigns can hope to get out of them","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"is firing up their base of voters","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"and lodging some good attacks on the opposition 's nominee .","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"On both those counts , Kaine hit his mark .","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"Voters","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"who care about criminal justice or immigration reform or even reproductive rights","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"will walk away","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"feeling good about the Clinton-Kaine ticket .","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"Voters","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"who worry about Trump 's shady business dealings or his coziness with Putin","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"were reminded of those concerns , repeatedly .","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"Kaine did n't leave Pence as a quivering mass of failure in the same way","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"that Clinton devastated Trump last week ,","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"but he did what he set out to do .","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"Now that that ordeal is over ,","depth":3},{"id":107,"text":"we can get back to far more important things ,","depth":3},{"id":108,"text":"including whether Clinton can wipe the floor with Trump yet again ,","depth":3},{"id":109,"text":"and finish him off for good , in Sunday 's town hall debate .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":219,"left":215,"right":218,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":215,"left":0,"right":214,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":214,